data.name: label3.Text
data.value: Edit the list of applications that you'd like to grant network access. Only applications in this list will be able to communicate. Use the Detect button to let TinyWall detect some software, or add applications manually.

data.name: label5.Text
data.value: Select special tasks or applications that you'd like to enable on this machine. Note that disabling recommended exceptions can seriously limit the usability and security of your system.

data.name: label9.Text
data.value: To remove an enabled password protection, check "Change password" and leave the text fields empty.

data.name: label10.Text
data.value: If you like and use this free program, please consider donating to cover hosting, hardware and software costs.
